name: Transelse
description:
Hello guys !

Please keep in mind that this is my first game ever made.

Transelse is (supposed to be) a 2D Bullet hell inspired by Transistor (because you can slow time). But the game doesn't look like my inspiration at all ! (sweaty smile)

Anyway, i really enjoyed this game jam and i hope i'll be able to participate another one soon !

Panpan
